Package: ShannonEntropy
Type: Package
Title: Shannon Entropy Estimation from Frequency Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Adel", "Fatemi",
      email = "adelfatemy@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides functions to calculate Shannon entropy 
    from categorical data. The package computes frequency tables,
    probability distributions, and Shannon entropy with natural 
    or custom logarithm bases. Handles missing values and follows 
    the convention 0*log(0)=0.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
